Text: Bowl PoolPST If you are not interested in getting into a College Football Bowl Pool just please delete this message now so I dont waste any more of your time If you ARE interested please go to this site to read about this years College Bowl Pool tjaecklebowlpoolhtm Everything you need to know is listed there I did this pool for the first time last year we had about people in it and it adds just a little more excitement to each bowl game for you Feel free to get some friends in if you think they might be interested Entry fee is Torrey Jaeckle
